.PP
\fBNotes:\fP
.IP \(bu 2
\fBclj\fP refers to the bare \fBclojure\fR CLI REPL without third-party
tools.
With rebel-readline, clj gains completion, multiline editing, and
syntax highlighting.
.IP \(bu 2
\fBbb\fP refers to Babashka v1.12+ which uses JLine3 for its console
REPL.
.IP \(bu 2
\fBlein repl\fP uses REPL-y (JLine-based) for its console interface.

